{"title_page": "Mia Malkova", "text_new": "{{short description|Pedda pornographic actress}}\n{{Multiple issues|\n{{More citations needed|date= October 2017}}\n{{Lead too short|date= October 2017}}\n}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Mia Malkova\n| image              = Mia Malkova 2016.jpg\n| caption            = Malkova at the AVN Expo in January 2016\n| birth_name         = \n| birth_date         = {{birth date and age|1992|07|01}}\n| birth_place        = [[Palm Springs, California]], U.S.<ref name=AVNInterview>{{cite web |url=http://business.avn.com/articles/video/Mia-Malkova-Wins-Twistys-Treat-of-the-Year-516033.html |title=Mia Malkova Wins Twistys Treat of the Year |accessdate=December 4, 2013 |author=Buzz Killington |date=May 3, 2013 |publisher=[[AVN (magazine)|AVN]]}}</ref>\n| spouse             = \n| height             = 5 ft 7 in<ref name=AVNInterview/>\n| occupation         = [[Pornographic film actress]]\n| alias              = Mia Bliss, Madison Swan, Jessica<ref name=IAFD>{{iafd name|id=miamalkova|gender=female|name=Mia Malkova}}</ref>\n}}\n\n'''Mia Malkova''' (born July 1, 1992) is an American [[pornographic actress]]<ref name=IAFD/> and [[Twitch (service)|Twitch]] streamer. She is the subject of the 2018 [[India]]n [[Documentary film|documentary]] film ''[[God, Sex and Truth]]''.\n\n==Career==\n\nPrior to entering the adult industry, Malkova worked in the food service industry getting her first job at [[McDonald's]] when she turned 16 and then working at [[Sizzler]] up until the weekend she shot her first scene.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://miamalkova.info/interview/|title=Interview|date=October 6, 2016}}</ref> Malkova was \u2018Twistys Treat of the Month\u2018 in December 2012 and the 2013 \u2018Twistys Treat of the Year\u2019.<ref name=AVNInterview/><ref name=TwistysTreat>{{cite web |url=http://business.avn.com/company-news/Mia-Malkova-Seeks-Fan-Aid-While-Running-for-Twistys-Treat-of-the-Year-513659.html |title=Mia Malkova Seeks Fan Aid While Running for Twistys Treat of the Year |accessdate=December 4, 2013 |date=April 18, 2013 |publisher=[[AVN (magazine)|AVN]]}}</ref> She was a contract performer for its parent company, [[Mindgeek]], during that time period.<ref name=\"contract\">{{cite news|last1=Warren|first1=Peter|title=Mia Malkova Becomes First Hard X Contract Performer {{!}} AVN|url=https://avn.com/business/articles/video/mia-malkova-becomes-first-hard-x-contract-performer-577973.html|accessdate=December 22, 2017|work=AVN|date=October 24, 2014}}</ref> When that contract lapsed in 2014, she signed a contract with another company, Hard X, to exclusively perform scenes with men while being allowed to perform scenes without men with other companies.<ref name=\"contract\" />\n\nMalkova is the focus of the 2018 documentary film ''[[God, Sex and Truth]]'' about the strength of women sexuality and beauty. In an interview, she revealed that \"the only reason she got into porn is because she loves sex and the porn world is the safest and the best place to explore sex in all its forms.\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/news/ram-gopal-varma-mia-malkova-got-industry-because-she-loves-sex-396391|title=Ram Gopal Varma: Mia Malkova got into the industry because she loves sex|website=PINKVILLA}}</ref>\n\nIn December 2019 she and Hearthstone streamer [[Trump (video game player)|Trump]] released a duetto singing a song ''A Whole New World'' together.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.invenglobal.com/articles/10046/hearthstone-streamer-trump-records-disney-song-with-adult-star-mia-malkova|title=Hearthstone streamer Trump records Disney song with adult star Mia Malkova|website=www.invenglobal.com}}</ref>\n\nIn April 2020 Malkova and eleven other adult/former adult actresses appeared in the music video for the [[G-Eazy]] song \"Still Be Friends\". <ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o0MjKgb1Lp4</ref>\n\n==Personal life==\nMalkova is of French Canadian, German, and Irish background.<ref name=IAFD/> Her brother, Justin Hunt, is also a pornographic actor.<ref name=\"avninterview\">{{cite news|last1=Killington|first1=Buzz|title=Mia Malkova Wins Twistys Treat of the Year {{!}} AVN|url=https://avn.com/business/articles/video/mia-malkova-wins-twistys-treat-of-the-year-516033.html|accessdate=December 22, 2017|work=AVN|date=May 3, 2013}}</ref> \n\n==Filmography==\n\n===Web series===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|- style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n!scope=\"col\"| Year\n!scope=\"col\"| Title\n!scope=\"col\"| Role\n!scope=\"col\"| Director\n!scope=\"col\"| Producer\n!scope=\"col\"| Music by\n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2018\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[God, Sex and Truth]]'' <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehansindia.com/posts/index/Cinema/2018-01-27/Women-Praising-RGVs-GST/354725|title=Women Praising RGV's GST!|website=The Hans India}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gFLVToNKBgY|title=YouTube|website=www.youtube.com}}</ref>\n| Mia Malkova <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.outlookindia.com/website/story/pornstar-mia-malkovas-god-sex-and-truth-released-director-rgv-says-watch-it-with/307429|title=Pornstar Mia Malkova's 'God, Sex And Truth' Released, Director RGV Says Watch It With Good Quality Headphones|publisher=}}</ref>\n|[[Ram Gopal Varma]]\n|Strike Force LLC\n|  [[M. M. Keeravani]]\n| Released on January 27, 2018 <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.godsextruthmovie.com/|title=STRIKE FORCE, LLC: watch|website=STRIKE FORCE, LLC|access-date=January 29, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614214004/http://godsextruthmovie.com/|archive-date=June 14, 2018|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Ceremony\n!Result\n!Award\n!Work\n|-\n|rowspan=\"12\"|2014\n|rowspan=\"7\"|[[AVN Award]]\n|{{won}}\n|Best All-Girl Group Sex Scene <small>(with Gracie Glam and Raven Rockette)</small><ref name=AVN14WINS>